      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Unfortunately, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Rise of the Third Power",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "’s pixel art graphics, despite how clean it is, can make it difficult to find the next screen and progress. I noticed this twice, once in the Pirate’s Cove within the game’s opening hour due to the entrances to the side of the screen being difficult to notice.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The second issue was when trying to find a torn piece of paper within a certain town, without realising what I was actually needing to look for. I spent a good amount of time just stumbling around lost; I then sent a message to one of the developers on their Discord who thankfully pointed me in the right direction. Other than these minor inconveniences (which could be nullified once guides come out for ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Rise of the Third Power",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "), there is nothing else of note that I found negative to my experience.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
